desc_long							评测						“I want more. This is usually a good indicator of a game quality.”Game Side Story“Wild Frontera offers some incredibly fun gameplay and is a solid Western shooter, unapologetically cliché and a non-stop chaotic adventure”7.5/10 – OKgames“Buy it, definitely buy it and have fun”ZombieNinjaPirate													最新更新									 "The rejuvenating elixir patch" Blasting cutthroats and sheeps come back in force with our summer updateTry to reach a 5 stars wanted level in the new Free Roam mode and stay alive the longer you can. And don't forget to choose the big head mode and Pluto's gravity while doing so :)  Frame rate improvements  Pad controls are rebindable from the control/pad option menu  Multiplayer score screen is now hidden on end game credits  You can press Start to leave the ingame menu  Some checkpoints requiring all players to be present have been altered to prevent getting stuck in co-op  Cursor mode with pad is now switchable with the directional pad down button  New dual wield animation with the revolver  You can now host a co-op game if no internet without getting kicked back to the menu  Custom settings for co-op servers :The following settings can be altered before creating a game server ( you can play solo on your own server) Player hit-pointsStarting weapon typeStarting weapon gradeMoney drop modifierCamera orientationBullet kinetic forceWeapon ConditionBase Player statsGravityNight modeBig head mode A new game mode called "Free roam" has been added. Allowing players to go wherever they want and cause mayhem by killing non aggro npcs and dealing with reinforcement  Fog and ambient map transition have been improved in some area  Some bandits change position less often when shooting at players  New landscape particle effects																						关于这款游戏							Wild Frontera is a top-down action shooter set in a western-fantasy worldYou are a lonesome gunslinger, that will have to get rid of hordes of enemies and defeat spectacular bosses in order to escape to the frontier.Armed with a rusty six-shooter that you can swap very quickly for new weapons, for a fistfull of dollars looted while playing the game.Ultra fast single-action revolvers.Long-range rifles with impressive damage. Or, if subtlety is not your forte, devastating shotguns : deadly in close quarter combat but leaving you with a very small margin of error.Fun, nervous and difficult, Wild Frontera offers non stop action, worthy of the best western movies, where every detail is a nod to the spaghetti genreYou will encounter stereotypical villains, outlaws, wild bloodthirsty animals and more...You'll travel across grasslands, the darkest forests, fields of bones, deserts, a gold mine and towns  in order to escape this crazy country and discover why you are now the most wanted bandito in the wild west.FeaturesPlay solo or online co-op up to 4 players8 stages with 17 boss fightsMouse / keyboard and gamepad twin-stick supportProcedurally generated weaponsOnline leaderboards for single player runsChallenging gameplay with fast respawn checkpoint systemGreenlightWild Frontera was submitted on Steam's Greenlight last july and was greenlit by the community in less than 10 days.The game was made by 2 passionate developers in 12 months.						
